text: Oksana Knizhnik (born 3 January 1977) is a Ukrainian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kyiv
